PrecisDirect the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to establish an office of the Commission in certain regions of Canada which are British Columbia/Yukon; Alberta/Northest Territories; Manitoba/Saskatchewan; Ontario; Quebec; and Atlantic region, whish encompasses Nova Scotia, New Brunswick, Prince Edward Island and Newfoundland.
